room_title: Escape room "Special Agent" by Escape Room Marlton in Collingswood
room_description: As a group of elite special agents, you have been tasked with infiltrating an enemy data center to retrieve vital information. Once inside, you discover they knew you were coming, and have left you a “surprise”! You have 60 minutes to retrieve the data and escape before their devious trap puts an end to your mission, and your agents' lives!
